Step 4.

I've added a few new features to SimFinger that we needed over here at Improbable Sciences. 
Activating Caps Lock will hide the 'finger' while you're recording with a nice fade in/fade out animation.
Additionally, you can constrain the pointer overlay to the iPhone's screen.